  <h1>Slow Squeezing System (SSS&trade;)</h1>

  <img src="/images/separation.png" class="left"/>
  <p>The Hurom Slow Squeezing System juices without friction or impact.
    The technology, exclusive to Hurom, gently presses the fruit in low speed, minimising
    the loss of nutrients by heat and oxidation in order to keep the natural taste and nutrition.</p>

  <h4>Higher nutrition and juice yield</h4>
  <p>The Hurom slow juicer not only produces twice as much as an ordinary juicer, but its juice contains four times the nutrients and six times the vitamins.
  </p>
